{"id":2814,"date":"2024-02-07T16:24:26","date_gmt":"2024-02-07T09:24:26","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/?p=2814"},"modified":"2024-05-08T23:05:44","modified_gmt":"2024-05-08T16:05:44","slug":"thong-bao-tuyen-sinh-trinh-do-thac-si-nganh-duoc-ly-va-duoc-lam-sang-nam-2024","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/thong-bao-tuyen-sinh-trinh-do-thac-si-nganh-duoc-ly-va-duoc-lam-sang-nam-2024\/","title":{"rendered":"TH\u00d4NG B\u00c1O TUY\u1ec2N SINH TR\u00ccNH \u0110\u1ed8 TH\u1ea0C S\u0128 NG\u00c0NH D\u01af\u1ee2C L\u00dd V\u00c0 D\u01af\u1ee2C L\u00c2M S\u00c0NG N\u0102M 2024"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u0103n c\u1ee9 Th\u00f4ng t\u01b0 s\u1ed1 23\/TT-BGD\u0110T c\u1ee7a B\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edfng B\u1ed9 Gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c v\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0o t\u1ea1o ng\u00e0y 30\/08\/2021 ban h\u00e0nh quy ch\u1ebf tuy\u1ec3n sinh v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ea1c s\u0129;<\/span><\/em><\/p>\n<p><em><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u0103n c\u1ee9 Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ed1 527\/Q\u0110-BGD\u0110T c\u1ee7a B\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edfng B\u1ed9 Gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c v\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0o t\u1ea1o ng\u00e0y 06\/02\/2024 cho ph\u00e9p Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o ng\u00e0nh D\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00fd v\u00e0 D\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e2m s\u00e0ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ea1c s\u0129.<\/span><\/em><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tuy\u1ec3n sinh tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ea1c s\u0129 ng\u00e0nh D\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00fd v\u00e0 D\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e2m s\u00e0ng n\u0103m 2024 nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>1.\u00a0\u00a0 H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c, th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 ng\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o: Ch\u00ednh quy<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o: 1,5 n\u0103m (h\u1ecdc bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i v\u00e0 th\u1ee9 7 h\u00e0ng tu\u1ea7n).<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>2.\u00a0\u00a0 \u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c tuy\u1ec3n sinh<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>2.1 \u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tuy\u1ec3n sinh<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">\u1ee8ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc (ho\u1eb7c tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u1edf l\u00ean) ng\u00e0nh D\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>2.2 Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c tuy\u1ec3n sinh: X\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">X\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 trung b\u00ecnh chung t\u00edch l\u0169y c\u1ee7a b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc: M\u1ee9c \u0111i\u1ec3m x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1eeb 2.0 tr\u1edf l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi H\u1ec7 4.0 v\u00e0 5.0 tr\u1edf l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi H\u1ec7 10.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>2.3 Y\u00eau c\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">\u1ee8ng vi\u00ean c\u00f3 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef t\u1eeb B\u1eadc 3 tr\u1edf l\u00ean theo Khung n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef 6 b\u1eadc \u00a0d\u00f9ng cho Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc tr\u1edf l\u00ean ng\u00e0nh ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i; ho\u1eb7c b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc tr\u1edf l\u00ean m\u00e0 ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu b\u1eb1ng ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i;<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 trong th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 02 n\u0103m t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y d\u1ef1 tuy\u1ec3n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t trong c\u00e1c v\u0103n b\u1eb1ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef \u0111\u1ea1t tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng B\u1eadc 3 tr\u1edf l\u00ean theo Khung n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef 6 b\u1eadc d\u00f9ng cho Vi\u1ec7t Nam ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1c do B\u1ed9 Gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c v\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0o t\u1ea1o c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 (<a href=\"https:\/\/drive.google.com\/file\/d\/1eXAfVL-vaOAOJ5YhO_2A-H2Cz3VYLB30\/view?usp=drive_link\"><strong>Ph\u1ee5 l\u1ee5c k\u00e8m theo<\/strong><\/a>), c\u00f2n hi\u1ec7u l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd d\u1ef1 tuy\u1ec3n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">*L\u01b0u \u00fd:<\/span> C\u00e1c v\u0103n b\u1eb1ng v\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc do c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i c\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00a0c\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng ti\u1ebfng Vi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 n\u1ed9p k\u00e8m theo v\u0103n b\u1ea3n x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn v\u0103n b\u1eb1ng c\u1ee7a C\u1ee5c Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, B\u1ed9 Gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c v\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0o t\u1ea1o.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>2.4 \u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110\u1ea1t y\u00eau c\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef: Tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ea5p B2 ho\u1eb7c h\u1ec7 4\/6 c\u1ee7a Khung tham chi\u1ebfu Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a B\u1ed9 Gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c v\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0o t\u1ea1o.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec1 \u00e1n theo Quy \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ea1c s\u0129 c\u1ee7a tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec1 \u00e1n t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea1t y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>3.\u00a0 Th\u1eddi gian nh\u1eadn h\u1ed3 s\u01a1, x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n, nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc.<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Nh\u1eadn h\u1ed3 s\u01a1: t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi gian x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ee3t.<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><em>\u0110\u1ee3t 1: <\/em><em>X\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n (d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn): <\/em>Ng\u00e0y <strong>1<\/strong><strong>1\/05<\/strong><strong>\/2024<\/strong>; <em>Nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc (d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn)<\/em>: <strong>2<\/strong><strong>5\/05<\/strong><strong>\/2024.<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><em>\u0110\u1ee3t 2: <\/em><em>X\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n (d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn): <\/em>Ng\u00e0y <strong>12\/10\/2024<\/strong>;<em> Nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc (d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn)<\/em>: <strong>2<\/strong><strong>6\/<\/strong><strong>1<\/strong><strong>0\/2024.<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><em>\u0110\u1ee3t <\/em><em>3<\/em><em>: <\/em><em>X\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n (d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn): <\/em>Ng\u00e0y <strong>14\/12\/2024<\/strong>;<em> Nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc (d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn)<\/em>: <strong>2<\/strong><strong>1\/<\/strong><strong>1<\/strong><strong>2\/2024<\/strong><strong>.<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>4. L\u1ec7 ph<\/strong><strong>\u00ed x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n<\/strong><strong>: 2.100.000 <\/strong>\u0111\u1ed3ng\/th\u00ed sinh, H\u1ed3 s\u01a1 mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>5. H\u1ed3 s\u01a1 bao g\u1ed3m<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Phi\u1ebfu \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd d\u1ef1 thi (theo m\u1eabu c\u1ee7a Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4);<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1ea3n sao c\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc;<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1ea3n sao CMT\/CCCD, gi\u1ea5y khai sinh;<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1ea3n sao c\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng c\u00e1c v\u0103n b\u1eb1ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">*Ghi ch\u00fa<\/span>: Kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n tr\u1ea3 h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 v\u00e0 l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed9p.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>6. \u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ed9p h\u1ed3 s\u01a1<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">* C\u00e1ch 1: Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1eddng ho\u1eb7c chuy\u1ec3n ph\u00e1t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec7n<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>V\u0103n ph\u00f2ng Trung t\u00e2m Tuy\u1ec3n sinh &#8211; <\/strong><strong>H<\/strong><strong>otline<\/strong><strong>: <\/strong><strong>0934.078.668, 02433.861.601<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u1ea7ng 1, Nh\u00e0 A, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Km 15, Qu\u1ed1c l\u1ed9 32, Kim Chung, Ho\u00e0i \u0110\u1ee9c, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">* C\u00e1ch 2: Tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i <\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>Website:<\/strong> <a href=\"http:\/\/www.thanhdo.edu.vn\">www.tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn<\/a><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>Fanpage: <\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/truongdaihocthanhdo\">https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/truongdaihocthanhdo<\/a><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>C\u0103n c\u1ee9 Th\u00f4ng t\u01b0 s\u1ed1 23\/TT-BGD\u0110T c\u1ee7a B\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1